arrangement.p:
The records are arranged in the 13 series:

Series I. Administrative Records, 1841-1972; 

Series II. Minutes, 1856-1959; 

Series III. Correspondence, 1881-1971; 

Series IV. Scrapbooks, 1863-1901; 

Series V. Members; 

Series VI. Initiations, 1884-1971; 

Series VII. Programs and Events, 1873-1988; 

Series VIII. Music and Poetry, 1874-1945; 

Series IX. Clippings, 1891-1957;

Series X. Publications, 1855-1953; 

Series XI. Photographs, 1870-1885; 

Series XII. Other Records, 1840-1933; and 

Series XIII. Architectural Drawings, May 1891.
